html
  head
  body
    p Trigger sign in by redirecting to:
    ul
      - each conn in connections 
        li connection=#{conn.name} (notice the connection param at the end)
        a(href='#{tenant_domain}/authorize?response_type=#{callbackOnHash ? 'token' : 'code'}&scope=openid%20profile&client_id=#{clientID}&redirect_uri=#{callback}&connection=#{conn.name}')
          pre.
              #{tenant_domain}/authorize?
              response_type=#{callbackOnHash ? 'token' : 'code'}
              &scope=openid%20profile
              &client_id=#{clientID}
              &redirect_uri=#{callback}
              &connection=#{conn.name}